      <title>葡萄牙总统将于 3 月 12 日至 20 日会见各方，然后再任命总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/portugal-president-to-meet-parties-march-12-20-before-naming-pm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙总统马塞洛·雷贝洛·德索萨将于 3 月 12 日至 3 月 20 日会见议会各党派，这是周日大选后任命新总理的过程的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/portugal-president-to-meet-parties-march-12-20-before-naming-pm</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 13:09:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯考虑在选举后加税以资助乌克兰战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/russia-weighs-tax-hikes-to-fund-war-in-ukraine-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于乌克兰战争给政府金库带来越来越大的压力，俄罗斯正在考虑大幅增税的方案，以筹集多达 4 万亿卢布（440 亿美元）的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/russia-weighs-tax-hikes-to-fund-war-in-ukraine-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 13:05:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普捍卫关税，否认采取报复行动的威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/trump-defends-tariffs-dismisses-threat-of-retaliatory-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普为其连任时提高对中国进口商品关税的计划进行了辩护，称他不介意中国是否对美国商品征收关税进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/trump-defends-tariffs-dismisses-threat-of-retaliatory-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 12:58:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
